<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

	<main class="info-page-main">
		<section class="found-archive" aria-labelledby="lost-found-title">
			<header class="archive-heading">
				<p class="notice-kicker">Recovered from the reeds, mud, and one confused heron</p>
				<h1 id="lost-found-title">Lost &amp; Found</h1>
				<p>To claim an object, describe it convincingly to the desk toad. Bribes of flies are frowned upon but
					effective.</p>
			</header>

			<div class="found-grid">
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/left-sock.png"
						alt="One left sock" />
					<div>
						<h2>One left sock</h2>
						<p>Still damp. Smells faintly of adventure.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/golden-crown.png"
						alt="A tiny golden crown" />
					<div>
						<h2>A tiny golden crown</h2>
						<p>Toad-sized. No questions, please.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/diary.png"
						alt="Waterproof diary" />
					<div>
						<h2>Waterproof diary</h2>
						<p>Features suspicious bite marks and one very dramatic doodle.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/cursed-spoon.png"
						alt="Cursed spoon" />
					<div>
						<h2>Cursed spoon</h2>
						<p>Probably cursed. Definitely a spoon.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/pebbles.png"
						alt="Three identical pebbles" />
					<div>
						<h2>Three identical pebbles</h2>
						<p>They insist they have never met.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/dignity.png"
						alt="Folded towel" />
					<div>
						<h2>Somebody’s dignity</h2>
						<p>Folded neatly beside the jumping rock.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/moss-key.png"
						alt="A moss-covered key" />
					<div>
						<h2>A moss-covered key</h2>
						<p>Opens something small, secret, or both.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/love-letter.png"
						alt="A love letter" />
					<div>
						<h2>One dramatic love letter</h2>
						<p>Addressed simply: “To the frog by the moonlit log.”</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/water-bottle.png"
						alt="Suspicious Bottle" />
					<div>
						<h2>“Probably pond water”</h2>
						<p>One stoppered bottle. Contents refuse to comment.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="found-item"><img class="found-item-image" src="/images/lost-items/snail-license.png"
						alt="A snail’s racing license" />
					<div>
						<h2>A snail’s racing license</h2>
						<p>Expired, somehow, in a hurry.</p>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>